freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Nerve pain in right hand, of 2nd and 3rd metacarpal phalangeal joint, and in the 2nd metacarpal area.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Loss of appetite.  Ate soup for lunch.

Swelling of left axillary lymph nodes -yesterday and today.
Symptoms have since resolved.  Fatigue is only remaining symptom.
